{"tid":1653564,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(召喚誠哥) Now TV是由電訊盈科全資擁有！","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:51:50.000Z","uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bff150585dee95ce26a9dbe1f8c73743296f87b8","tid":1653564,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Now TV是香港的收費電視台，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由電訊盈科全資擁有</span>的電訊盈科媒體負責經營 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">代表人物 李澤楷！！！<br />\n<br />\n求誠哥出聲<br />\n</span><br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nNow新聞台強烈譴責警方　車長稱警署內遭暴力對待<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台發表聲明，對有車長凌晨在旺角警署附近取採訪車時，懷疑中布袋彈受傷，並被警員帶入警署扣查事件，表示極度遺憾，並強烈譴責警方濫用武力。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，該車長受傷倒地後，仍被按在地上綁上索帶，押返警署，表示極度遺憾，聲明又就車長在負傷情況下在警署內遭暴力對待，強烈譴責警方濫用武力，促請警方執法必須克制，並徹查事件。"},{"pid":"1424eb07cd1dc9c9065ddb1dd8d52ad916c626e2","tid":1653564,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b1e99a7c668e82827ea4e15caa994742777301","tid":1653564,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>信報記者比藍屍斬！<br />\nNow tv車長比黑警打！<br />\n<br />\n誠哥點忍啊？你自己d員工比人搞啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"265900825a21e395b4a27ceb9b22e6a2ba7a45f2","tid":1653564,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf0175857029ecaceafce95efba23969c16adaf","tid":1653564,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ece36341f0f5262fab9a96834466b84e2594d6","tid":1653564,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"